    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bedspreads, usually white and generally of cotton, with raised designs done either in weft loop weave or needlework, using a heavy thread resembling the wicks used by candlemakers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
